  | Domain     | What It Captures                     |
  |------------|--------------------------------------|
  | Tasks      | What I need to DO                    |
  | Events     | What I need to ATTEND/PARTICIPATE IN |
  | Habits     | What I need to REPEAT                |
  | Goals      | What I want to ACHIEVE               |
  | Principles | What I BELIEVE/VALUE                 |
  | Choices    | What I need to DECIDE                |
  | Finance    | What I SPEND/EARN                    |

  This is a complete ontology of action. When a user submits a journal, everything they say can be mapped to one of these seven domains. That's the foundational insight.

